quote.summary: Yibin City Commercial Bank Co Ltd is a China-based company primarily engaged in the operation of city commercial bank. The Company mainly operates its business through four segments. The Corporate Banking segment is engaged in providing corporate and institutional customers with financial products and services, including corporate loans, bill discounting and rediscounting, corporate deposits and fee- and commission-based products and services. The Retail Banking segment is engaged in providing products and services to retail banking customers, including loans, deposits, bank cards, and other fee- and commission-based services. The Financial Markets segment includes interbank market business and financial investment business. The Unallocated segment includes rental income and other miscellaneous income. The Company mainly conducts its business in the domestic market.
